author: alf
msg: Parameters used to build a POST body are encoded if specified, when it is application_x_www_form_urlencoded. This changes the behavior of PostWriter, so that HttpSampler works similar as HttpSampler2, after the SVN 582954 change to HttpSampler2.
Fix unit tests for parameter values as body, by telling the sampler to not encode parameters.
